title: 10 More Books - December 2015 (gnv64)
description:
Another collection of 10 books 7 PDF & 3 ePUB for this month. Covers included in a separate folder:


01. The Art of the Infinite - The Pleasures of Mathematics by Robert Kaplan and Ellen Kaplan
02. From Pythagoras to Einstein by K. 0. Friedrichs
03. Sherlock Holmes in Babylon and Other Tales of Mathematical History by Edited by Marlow Anderson, Victor Katz, Robin Wilson
04. Quantum Physics of Time - Cosmology, Brain, Mind, and Time Travel by Deepak Chopra, Giovanni Berlucchi et al
05. My Backyard Jungle - The Adventures of an Urban Wildlife Lover by James Barilla
06. Social Media for Writers - Marketing Strategies for Building Your Audience and Selling Books by Tee Morris & Pip Ballantine
07. The Great Christ Comet - Revealing the True Star of Bethlehem by Colin R. Nicholl
08. The Formation of the Solar System  - Theories Old and New (2nd Ed) by Michael  Woolfson
09. Magnificent Desolation - The Long Journey Home from the Moon by Buzz Aldrin with Ken Abraham
10. The Man Who Painted the Universe by Ron Legro, Avi Lank
